%!demo
%! ## `split` decomposes a calendar duration into the whole-unit components you
%! ## request, distributing the span across them.  (Contrast the single-unit
%! ## extractors such as `calmonths`, which each return the span as a *total* in
%! ## one unit.)
%!
%! d = calendarDuration (2, 3, 40)
%! [y, mo, days] = split (d, {'years', 'months', 'days'});
%! [y, mo, days]
